Package com.redis.foundation.data

Class DataRange

java.lang.Object
com.redis.foundation.data.DataRange
public class DataRange extends Object
A DataRange is used by DataItem to ensure that their values constrained to an enumerated list or range of values.
Since:
1.0
Author:
Al Cole
